propel.core.utils

Enum ScanSortMode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ScanSortMode>
      • propel.core.utils.ScanSortMode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ScanSortMode>

    public enum ScanSortMode
extends java.lang.Enum<ScanSortMode>
    The file/folder sort mode. Directories are ALWAYS ranked above files, this setting only adjusts the comparison used between folders with folders and files with files.
